This paper is about evolving deep neural networks for image classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) domains. The proposed method uses particle swarm optimization (PSO) to search for optimal CNN architectures, which is a type of evolutionary computation and thus falls under the neural networks (cs.NE) domain. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of transfer learning, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.SY.
